import React from "react"; export default function ProductStock() { return (
Name Email Password Active From Last Login Status {userList.map((row) => ( {row.Name} {row.Email} {row.Password} {row.ActiveFrom == null ? 'NILL' : row.ActiveFrom} {row.LastLogin == null ? 'NILL' : row.LastLogin} {row.Status == 1 ? "Enabled" : "Disabled"} ))}
) }
